DeathSteel::

He frowned slightly. He had never been called adiquate before and 
disapproved of the general's sudden assesment of him. He crossed his 
arms infront of his chest and looked at Tyrael. "So then, would you 
please continue with my debriefing? I wish to learn all that I can if 
I am to an,"  he looks at the general and then back to the 
hologram, "adiquate fighter in your ranks." With that, he sat back 
down and kept his arms crossed.
